==Useful Info==
'''Chaos champions''' are demonspawn who can smite you with chaos beams and cast [[Random Bolt]]s.  Their spell [[Call of Chaos]] applies (usually) positive status effects to nearby allies. They can be found in the [[Pandemonium]].

